CancelMatching.document: This API is used to cancel matching.

DescribeMatchCodes.document: This API is used to query the created MatchCodes and paginate the query result.

DescribeMatches.document: This API is used to query the matchmaking list and paginate the query result.

DescribeMatchingProgress.document: This API is used to query the matching progress.
DescribeMatchingProgress.name: Queries matching progress

DescribeRule.document: This API is used to query the rule details.

DescribeRules.document: This API is used to query the rule set list and paginate the query result.
DescribeRules.name: Queries the rule set list and paginates the query result

DescribeToken.document: This API is used to query the token of a Matchcode, which is used for verified the pushed message.

ModifyMatch.document: This API is used to modify a match.
ModifyMatch.name: Modifies a match

ModifyRule.document: This API is used to modify a rule (including description and tag).
ModifyRule.name: Modifies a rule

ModifyToken.document: This API is used to modify the token of a Matchcode.
ModifyToken.name: Modifies the token of a Matchcode

StartMatching.document: This API is used to pass in one player or multiple players to initiate match. Players within the same request will be assigned to the same game session.
StartMatching.name: Initiates match

StartMatchingBackfill.document: This API is used to send a match backfill request, for which a MatchTicket will be searched to start a new match.
StartMatchingBackfill.name: Initiates a match backfill request
